BRAF-V600E SKCM cell lines:
  A375 (BRAF V600E), SK-MEL-28 (BRAF V600E), SK-MEL-5 (BRAF V600E),
  COLO800 (BRAF V600E), UACC257 (BRAF V600E), LOXIMVI (BRAF V600E),
